high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the apple off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink and look up at the microwave.
Microwave the apple for a couple seconds to heat it up, and then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated apple inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Heat the apple in the microwave above the sink.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge, in front and to the left of the gray bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in a fridge.

high_descs: pick up the apple from the table
turn around and head to the oven
cool the apple in the oven and take it out
turn around and head to the fridge
place the cooked apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a cooked apple in the fridge
